                ],
                "institute": "2ITYMIL"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " AVF cyclotron.",
                "The AVF cyclotron was a negative ions (H-) machine,",
                "with a thin Al stripping foil extraction system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A beam current of about 100 Na and an integrated",
                "charge varying from 200 to 400 mCoulomb."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
